caption: Mara, a young influencer, takes her followers on a haunted beach trip during Halloween in the remote town of San Juan del Norte, Colombia, sharing spooky pumpkins, cobwebs, and a lighthouse skeleton with a twilight glow. Her post shows a low-angle shot capturing the misty horizon and vibrant color palette of deep blue, gold, and purple. #SpookyTravel #HalloweenInfluencer #BeachAdventure
